data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Since the very beginning of Script-o-matic, we have provided a community with information and tools free of charge. To this very day, we still provide the same. However, since personal circumstances have changed and the fact the community isn't as strong anymore - it is becoming difficult to support Script-o-matic and other misc. projects.
If you've either gained something from Script-o-matic, or just simply enjoyed helping and supporting the community, consider donating to us. It helps pay server and domain costs, as well as encourage future projects (or you can buy us a beer by donating...). Enjoy this release!
